{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Valdis is a bullet-hell-adventure game set in the fantasy world of a fallen Empire. The hero will start off as a fledgling pirate, and explore the seas of the Valdis region. Will you be the one to rise victorious and open the Legendary Vault?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/extras/combat2.gif?t=1729722002\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat in Valdis is a fast paced bullet hell. You will dodge and weave projectiles and shoot off your own Davon Light Stone Cannon. The amount of hearts you will have in battles is based on your crew count, so be sure to recruit more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/extras/map2.png?t=1729722002\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arriving in Valdis in a small pirate vessel, you will get to explore the oceans and islands of Valdis. You can obtain treasure maps, which will point to hidden treasures. You will also have access to multiple different compasses, helping you navigate the seas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/extras/cat1b.png?t=1729722002\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The settlements and islands are populated with NPC:s, who will tell their own stories and give you quests. The cat in question is Master Minttu.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729722002","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729722002","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600810/52946bc750a63459bbaf15caa63d7e95ffaab125/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729722002","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.